## Vue Blog App
A simple blogging app created using Vue, Express and MongoDB
Uses an Atlas sandbox at mongodb.com

run:
> npm run dev



### Testing POST without any front end
Using Git Bash:
> curl --request POST --header "Content-Type: application/json"  --data '{"text":"I am learning Curl"}' localhost:3000/api/posts
> curl -X DELETE localhost:3000/api/posts/60a592751c83c23b18403b19

Using Windows Powershell:
> curl --% --request POST --header "Content-Type: application/json" --data  "{\"text\":\"I like Vue\"}" localhost:3000/api/posts
(on Win 10 you may need to run > Remove-item alias:curl )

